#: ../../../release_details/9.5/fix-composite-mapper-opacity-override.md:1
msgid "Fix vtkCompositePolyDataMapper opacity override"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/fix-composite-mapper-opacity-override.md:3
msgid ""
"You can now render opaque blocks in a composite dataset even when the actor "
"has an opacity < 1.0 by setting the opacity of the block equal to 1.0. "
"Previously, a bug in vtkActor prevented the overridden block's opacity value "
"from being considered when the actor was transparent."
msgstr ""

